 is-editor-empty\"><span style=\"color: rgb(194, 30, 86);\"><strong>Her</strong></span> voice was soft, almost trembling.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"><span style=\"color: rgb(194, 30, 86);\"><strong>She</strong></span> asked <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong>you</stron","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"yj0sMtlEuFJIZD0yAGiP2.webp","creator":"Franzzzzzzzzz","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","👩‍🦰 Female","🧑‍🎨 OC","👭 Multiple","👤 AnyPOV","💔 Angst"],"chats":1529,"messages":23672,"created_at":"2025-11-22T09:14:12.453602+00:00"}